WEBVTT

00:00:27.906 --> 00:00:30.216
But there is something

00:00:30.216 --> 00:00:32.109
which touches.

00:00:36.111 --> 00:00:38.021
There are some stories

00:00:42.159 --> 00:00:45.199
which bring us closer

00:00:47.219 --> 00:00:49.769
(Applause)

00:00:49.769 --> 00:00:53.521
Shah Rukh Khan: On TED Talks India, 
people the world over not only share ideas

00:00:53.521 --> 00:00:56.847
but they do so in a way
that they share their life stories.

00:00:56.871 --> 00:00:59.252
Today we have with us
one such young storyteller,

00:00:59.276 --> 00:01:02.007
who has heard stories
from Uttaranchal to Afghanistan,